creator: PLAYDOG
descriptionHtml:
Don't you dream of becoming the main character of a famous restaurant in the world someday? That dream might come true in TastyVille!
Be the main character, decorate your own restaurant and sell various dishes. Create a world that is filled with colors in the one and only TastyVille!


♡♥Features of TastyVille♥♡

1. Design your own restaurant!
- Use decorations earned from clearing stages to decorate your restaurant!
- Place decorations that customers want and attract more customers!

2. Manage restaurants with various concepts!
- From street carts to large restaurants with staff, enjoy the fun of growth!
- What kind of restaurant will you open next? Create your own brand with your own style!

3. Hire and manage unique staff!
- Upgrading employee grades is essential to increase their efficiency!
- Help staff who are low on stamina or slacking off to get back to work!

4. Addictive match-3 puzzles that pop and burst!
- Solve unique and fun match-3 puzzles!
- Enjoy various decorations and new menu items earned from clearing stages!

5. Experience a captivating journey and become the protagonist of TastyVille!
- Uncover wonderful and endearing surprises of Amelia's life!
- Meet various characters, have conversations, and enjoy their stories!
Look forward to meeting more unique characters in the future!

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Are you having fun playing TastyVille? Learn more about the game!
